35double QwtSplineParametrization::valueIncrement(
36 const QPointF& point1, const QPointF& point2 ) const
37{
38 switch( m_type )
39 {
40 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterX:
41 {
42 return valueIncrementX( point1, point2 );
43 }
44 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterY:
45 {
46 return valueIncrementY( point1, point2 );
47 }
48 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterCentripetal:
49 {
50 return valueIncrementCentripetal( point1, point2 );
51 }
52 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterChordal:
53 {
54 return valueIncrementChordal( point1, point2 );
55 }
56 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterManhattan:
57 {
58 return valueIncrementManhattan( point1, point2 );
59 }
60 case QwtSplineParametrization::ParameterUniform:
61 {
62 return valueIncrementUniform( point1, point2 );
63 }
64 default:
65 {
66 return 1;
67 }
68 }
69}
